apps.localizedDescription:
Cluckabunga allows users to tweak their device without a jailbreak using KFD on iOS 16.2 - 16.5 & 16.6 beta 1.

Custom themes for apps, hiding docks,and more!

*This is different from Cowabunga, and also Cluckabunga has less features.*
apps.name: Cluckabunga
apps.subtitle: A device tweaker using the KFD exploit on iOS 16.2 - 16.5 & 16.6 beta 1.

apps.localizedDescription: Filza is a file manager that allows you to copy or delete files from your device. You can also view system files and more.
apps.name: Filza
apps.subtitle: File Manager for iOS 12+.

apps.localizedDescription:
Misaka is a device tweaker for iOS 15 - 16.6.1 that uses an MDC & KFD exploit.

It consists of 24 default repos & lots of tweaks without a jailbreak.
apps.name: Misaka
apps.subtitle: A device tweaker for iOS 15 - 16.6.1.
apps.versionDescription:
Fixed Crash Bug (8.2.3 - )
Fixed Icon Theme Manager
License (ColorfulX)
There will probably be no update until the new kernel exploit is released.

apps.localizedDescription:
Cowabunga allows users to tweak their device without a jailbreak using MDC on iOS 15 - 16.1.2.

Status Bar Changer, Themes, Passcode Face Changer, Whitelist Feature, JIT, Remove 3 App Limit, and more!
apps.name: Cowabunga
apps.subtitle: A device tweaker using the MDC exploit on iOS 15 - 16.1.2.
apps.versionDescription: Changing carrier bar strength now works when you do not have a sim card (or dual sim for secondary carrier)

apps.localizedDescription:
Removes the three app limit on iOS 14 - 16.1.2 (excluding 15.7.2).

Keep in mind you are still limited to 10 App ID's.
apps.name: WDBRemoveThreeAppLimit
apps.subtitle: Remove the three app limit.

apps.localizedDescription:
This app installs TrollStore for devices running iOS 14 - 16.6.1.

*A8(X) iPads are only supported on iOS 14 - 15.1*
apps.name: TrollInstallerX
apps.subtitle: TrollStore Installer for iOS 14 - 16.6.1
apps.versionDescription:
- Update for Xcode 15.4+ compilation (fixes #25)
Added a temporary fix for yellow iPhone 14 (Plus) devices on iOS 16.3, please use TrollInstallerX-20D50.ipa (fixes #33)
Removing confusing logging around exploit deinitialisation (e.g. #11)
Fix arm64e devices on iOS 15.7.x that couldn't download the kernelcache by updating libgrabkernel2 (should, in theory, fix #21)
Note: A8 devices on iOS 15.2+ will not be supported until a future release of TrollInstallerX. Furthermore, support for arm64e (A12+) devices on early iOS 17.0 betas is not planned, unless someone else would like to implement it. You can now use TrollRestore for both of these cases.

apps.localizedDescription: PureKFD is a tweak customizer for iOS 14 - 18 beta1, which uses 3 exploits, MDC, KFD and SparseRestore. You can install tweaks without jailbreaking your device.
apps.name: PureKFD
apps.subtitle: A device tweaker for iOS 14+

apps.localizedDescription: Dopamine is a jailbreak for iOS 15 - 16.5.1 on A12+ and iOS 15 - 16.6.1 on ARM64.
apps.name: Dopamine
apps.subtitle: A jailbreak for iOS 15 - 16.5.1 on ARM64e and iOS 15 - 16.6.1 on ARM64.

apps.localizedDescription: TrollApps is a sideloading app that is installed using TrollStore, and provides a built-in repo system and many more other features, such as installing apps using URL schemes.
apps.name: TrollApps
apps.subtitle: A sideloading app paired with TrollStore.

apps.localizedDescription: UTM-SE is a virtual machine emulator, capable of running Linux, Windows or any operaing system. UTM is based off of QEMU. *UTM-SE does not use JIT and is slower. For jailbroken users or TrollStore users, use UTM-TS or normal UTM.
apps.name: UTM-SE
apps.subtitle: A virtual machine emulator based off of QEMU for iOS & MacOS.

apps.localizedDescription: TrollBox is a tweak customizer for iOS 14 - 16.1.2 and uses a MDC exploit. It has features like AirDrop Spammer, Location Simulator, and more.
apps.name: TrollBox
apps.subtitle: A device tweaker for iOS 14 - 16.1.2.
apps.versionDescription: Development has stopped and is archived.

apps.localizedDescription: UTM-SE is a virtual machine emulator, capable of running Linux, Windows or any operaing system. UTM is based off of QEMU. *This version requires TrollStore. Otherwise, use UTM-SE for normal devices or UTM for jailbroken devices/JIT.
apps.name: UTM-TS (HV)
apps.subtitle: A virtual machine emulator based off of QEMU for iOS & MacOS.
apps.versionDescription: Development has stopped and is archived.

apps.localizedDescription: A full-featured bootstrap for iOS 15 - 17 on A8 - A17 & M1/M2. This is not a full jailbreak and not all tweaks will work. Must be installed using TrollStore.
apps.name: Roothide Bootstrap
apps.subtitle: A full-featured bootstrap for iOS 15 - 17.

apps.localizedDescription: Dopamine is a jailbreak for iOS 15 - 16.5.1 on ARM64e and iOS 15 - 16.6.1 on ARM64. Roothide Dopamine prevents jailbreak detection, be certain tweaks need to be complied to work with roothide. This must be installed with TrollStore.
apps.name: Roothide Dopamine
apps.subtitle: A roothide-based jailbreak for iOS 15 - 16.5.1 on ARM64 and iOS 15 - 16.6.1 on ARM64e.
